<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <title>Redefinir Senha</title>
  </head>

  <body
    style="
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      font-family:
        -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
    "
  >
    <table
      role="presentation"
      cellspacing="0"
      cellpadding="0"
      border="0"
      width="100%"
      style="background-color: #f5f5f5"
    >
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 40px 20px">
          <!-- Container Principal -->
          <table
            role="presentation"
            cellspacing="0"
            cellpadding="0"
            border="0"
            width="600"
            style="
              margin: 0 auto;
              background-color: #ffffff;
              border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
              border-radius: 8px;
            "
          >
            <!-- Conteúdo -->
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 60px 50px">
                <table
                  role="presentation"
                  cellspacing="0"
                  cellpadding="0"
                  border="0"
                  width="100%"
                >
                  <!-- Logo -->
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding-bottom: 40px; font-weight: 600">
                      APP
                    </td>
                  </tr>

                  <!-- Título -->
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding-bottom: 24px">
                      <h1
                        style="
                          margin: 0;
                          color: #000000;
                          font-size: 28px;
                          font-weight: 600;
                          line-height: 1.3;
                        "
                      >
                        Redefinir sua Senha
                      </h1>
                    </td>
                  </tr>

                  <!-- Texto -->
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding-bottom: 32px">
                      <p
                        style="
                          margin: 0;
                          color: #525252;
                          font-size: 16px;
                          line-height: 1.5;
                        "
                      >
                        Recebemos uma solicitação para redefinir a senha da sua
                        conta APP. Clique no botão abaixo para criar uma nova
                        senha.
                      </p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>

                  <!-- Botão -->
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding-bottom: 40px">
                      <table
                        role="presentation"
                        cellspacing="0"
                        cellpadding="0"
                        border="0"
                      >
                        <tr>
                          <td
                            style="
                              border-radius: 6px;
                              background-color: #0066ff;
                            "
                          >
                            <a
                              href="<%=resetUrl%>"
                              target="_blank"
                              style="
                                display: inline-block;
                                padding: 12px 24px;
                                font-family:
                                  -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI',
                                  Arial, sans-serif;
                                font-size: 15px;
                                font-weight: 500;
                                color: #ffffff;
                                text-decoration: none;
                                border-radius: 6px;
                              "
                            >
                              Redefinir Senha
                            </a>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </table>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 20px 0; border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee">
                      <p
                        style="
                          margin: 0 0 10px 0;
                          color: #999999;
                          font-size: 14px;
                          line-height: 1.6;
                        "
                      >
                        Se o botão não funcionar, copie e cole o seguinte link
                        no seu navegador:
                      </p>
                      <p
                        style="
                          margin: 0;
                          color: #667eea;
                          font-size: 14px;
                          word-break: break-all;
                        "
                      >
                        <%=resetUrl%>
                      </p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>

                  <!-- Footer -->
                  <tr>
                    <td>
                      <table
                        role="presentation"
                        cellspacing="0"
                        cellpadding="0"
                        border="0"
                        width="100%"
                      >
                        <tr>
                          <td style="padding-right: 20px">
                            <p
                              style="
                                margin: 0;
                                color: #000000;
                                font-size: 14px;
                                font-weight: 500;
                              "
                            >
                              Stroopwafel
                            </p>
                          </td>
                          <td style="text-align: right">
                            <a
                              href="#"
                              style="
                                color: #999999;
                                font-size: 14px;
                                text-decoration: none;
                              "
                            >
                              Cancelar subscrição destes emails
                            </a>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </table>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>

          <table
            role="presentation"
            cellspacing="0"
            cellpadding="0"
            border="0"
            width="600"
            style="margin: 20px auto 0"
          >
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 0 50px">
                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0;
                    color: #999999;
                    font-size: 12px;
                    line-height: 1.5;
                  "
                >
                  Se não solicitou, pode ignorar este email com segurança.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
